{"tid":1072224,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朱晨麗罕有地穿上運動Bra Top配襯短褲","createTime":"2019-03-22T01:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T10:08:22.000Z","uid":3747,"like":3,"dislike":104,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"635943d739dc030cbd0a5fbcefb3302186b6187e","tid":1072224,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:33:42.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】朱晨麗昨日罕有地穿上運動Bra Top配襯短褲，為代言的瘦身產品拍攝廣告，身材Fit爆。問到拍攝前是否要特別花工夫保養？她坦言沒有做過甚 準備，因拍劇忙得連睡覺都沒有時間，更何況是抽時間做運動。她透露服用此產品近兩個月，大讚確有顯著功效，並謂：「我一直係咁食 ，拍劇拍20幾30個鐘，所以我都會照食 ，尤其是消夜，唔食 真係會暈。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，朱晨麗透露新劇《大醬園》即將開拍，對於往後數個月可跟緋聞男友何廣沛日對夜對，她笑道：「唉！諗起就頭痛，劇入面我 好多嗌交戲，要調節自己唔好太投入角色，怕真係會討厭佢。」文、圖：駱震寧<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"49ea5e987b7e16f6ede8b7669578665f321719d7","tid":1072224,"uid":44916,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:34:30.000Z","msg":"張圖好無美感"},{"pid":"01abb68808ecb065aa3047fd64d27aaa817bf005","tid":1072224,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:35:14.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"b2d1d1837a41c12b54807e70ea630513ef42c008","tid":1072224,"uid":103914,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:36:25.000Z","msg":"肚臍有粒花柳"},{"pid":"4711ebf1b6e054f01599e138bb4d3fdf329a93bf","tid":1072224,"uid":153305,"like":46,"dislike":4,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"除咗對燈，冇乜嘢得"},{"pid":"e9dda02f42824b30c0541fcf7c633b8a9bced3b5","tid":1072224,"uid":186844,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acb66e58bbea3a726caec07595df632d98ce89d","tid":1072224,"uid":187076,"like":49,"dislike":4,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgEpK2g.gif\" dat